<guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hegseth-pushes-trumps-1-5-trillion-defense-budget-for-2027-as-congress-presses-pentagon-over-iran-war-costs/articleshow/131052298.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-13T06:39:55+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131052306,imgsize-1032959.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Who is Maya Higa? Twitch streamer makes history with first-ever TED Talk and standing ovation]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131052021.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Maya Higa made history by becoming the first Twitch streamer to deliver an official TED Talk, earning a standing ovation from the audience in Vancouver. During the speech, she spoke about using livestreaming to inspire animal conservation through her Alveus Animal Sanctuary. Maya revealed her community has raised over $7.5 million for conservation efforts since 2019. Fans and fellow creators praised the emotional moment online, calling it a major milestone for Twitch and digital creators.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/who-is-maya-higa-twitch-streamer-makes-history-with-first-ever-ted-talk-and-standing-ovation/articleshow/131052021.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/who-is-maya-higa-twitch-streamer-makes-history-with-first-ever-ted-talk-and-standing-ovation/articleshow/131052021.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-13T05:47:46+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131052021,imgsize-50620.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[What happened between Trevv and ChudTheBuilder? Nashville confrontation turns into aggravated robbery controversy]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131049818.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[ChudTheBuilder and Trevv’s online feud exploded after Trevv stole ChudTheBuilder’s hat during a public Nashville encounter on May 10, 2026. The situation quickly turned serious after accusations of aggravated robbery, weapon claims, and FBI comments surfaced online. Despite multiple viral posts and livestream reactions from both creators, no arrests or confirmed investigations have been publicly reported so far.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/what-happened-between-trevv-and-chudthebuilder-nashville-confrontation-turns-into-aggravated-robbery-controversy/articleshow/131049818.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/what-happened-between-trevv-and-chudthebuilder-nashville-confrontation-turns-into-aggravated-robbery-controversy/articleshow/131049818.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-13T03:26:14+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sehjal Gupta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131049810,imgsize-800871.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Row over Pete Davidson's 'dark humour' on Charlie Kirk: 'He constantly makes 9/11 jokes...']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131049412.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/row-over-pete-davidsons-dark-humour-on-charlie-kirk-he-constantly-makes-9/11-jokes-/articleshow/131049412.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/row-over-pete-davidsons-dark-humour-on-charlie-kirk-he-constantly-makes-9/11-jokes-/articleshow/131049412.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-13T02:14:41+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131049419,imgsize-84304.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Missing Indian man Sandarsh Krishna found dead in Grand Canyon, no cause of death established yet]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131049384.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/missing-indian-man-sandarsh-krishna-found-dead-in-grand-canyon-no-cause-of-death-established-yet/articleshow/131049384.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/missing-indian-man-sandarsh-krishna-found-dead-in-grand-canyon-no-cause-of-death-established-yet/articleshow/131049384.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-13T02:06:38+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131049402,imgsize-58014.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[D4vd appears relaxed in court during murder case status hearing in Los Angeles]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131049297.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Singer D4vd, David Burke, appeared in a Los Angeles courtroom for a status hearing in his murder case. Charged in connection with the death of 14-year-old Celeste Rivas Hernandez, Burke pleaded not guilty. Lawyers discussed evidence exchange and case timelines, with the next hearing set for June 17 and the preliminary hearing on June 29.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/d4vd-appears-relaxed-in-court-during-murder-case-status-hearing-in-los-angeles/articleshow/131049297.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://tim